  "summary": "Malicious code in siitoogether (PyPI)",
  "details": "\n---\n_-= Per source details. Do not edit below this line.=-_\n\n## Source: kam193 (6fccd687f1acb55e6da0782b08ef14b3e8be5587dee4743a163a106c48390a50)\nImporting the module starts an RAT-like process capable of execute remote commands, with the C2 through Discord\n\n\n---\n\nCategory: MALICIOUS - The campaign has clearly malicious intent, like infostealers.\n\n\nCampaign: 2025-11-siitoogether\n\n\nReasons (based on the campaign):\n\n\n - rat\n\n\n - The package contains code to execute remote commands (probably limited to a specific set) on the victim's machine.\n",
